import * as React from 'react'
import { Card, Text } from 'react-native-paper'

const CardLogin = (props) => (
  <Card>
    <Card.Content>
      <Text variant="titleLarge">{props.title}</Text>
      <Text variant="bodyMedium">Card content</Text>
    </Card.Content>
  </Card>
)

export default Card
